Anyway, to address Woow's most recent point, the most uber enchanter would not need at least 5 minutes to regen 900 mana.  c3 gives (according to Casters Realm) 14 per tick.  This is in addition to your natural mana tick and your Flowing Thought ticks.  The most uber chanter probably regens mana at around 20-25 per tick.  If you calculate JUST the 14 per tick, the maximum it would take is 4 minutes.  Factor in natural tick and FT's and it takes 2 minutes tops to get 900 mana back.  Add into account Theft of Thought.<br>
<br>
Is 1-2 minutes of your time worth 100pp?  /shrug<br>
